show.title: Mayakkamenna
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/Csa229
show.description: On our third wedding anniversary, my husband humiliated me and threw me away for his mistress. They thought I was powerless but they didn’t know I’m the daughter of the richest man in the country. His entire fortune came from me. That same day, fate led me to a powerful billionaire who changed everything. Now, I have wealth, influence, and a new identity. Let the tables turn.
